1934;;The Merry Widow;;American;;Ernst Lubitsch;;Jeanette MacDonald, Maurice Chevalier, Edward Everett Horton;;comedy, musical;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Merry_Widow_(1934_film);;Playboy Captain Danilo (Maurice Chevalier) is ordered by King Achmet of Marshovia (George Barbier) to court and marry Madame Sonia (Jeanette MacDonald), a rich widow who owns a large portion of the kingdom.